        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks him for book by Grant Allen [<hi rend="italic">Physiological aesthetics</hi> (1877)].</p> 
            <p>Comments on dispute over spontaneous generation.</p> 
<p>The Council [of the Royal Society] will not print Frank Darwin’s paper on <hi rend="italic">Dipsacus</hi> [in <hi rend="italic">Philos. Trans. R. Soc. Lond.</hi>].</p> 
            <p>Mentions GJR’s grafting experiments</p>
            <p>and his investigation of spiritualism.</p>
        </abstract>
